Mix the chopped mango, sliced kiwi and passion fruit pulp and seeds together in a large serving bowl.Sprinkle over the chopped stem ginger and mix well.Drizzle over the ginger syrup and squeeze over the lime juice. Mix carefully until the fruit is coated in the ginger and lime juice.To serve, spoon the matrimony de luxe into four shallow serving bowls. Drizzle over double cream or add a scoop of ice cream.